title: Arrest of Andrew, brother of King Charles, shakes the House of Windsor
summary_full: Unlike King Charles I, who was arrested in 1647, Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor will not be executed. But his legal woes and ties to Jeffrey Epstein threaten to damage the royal family.
